A good sauce pan is every cook's friend.  Both for boiling potatoes, and restoring order. Grab this pan, open one can of whoop-ass, and do lunch!

A control station for the equipment ahead. A warning is displayed on one of the screens:

"Warning - Heavy Water Extraction Site:

Not for use as drinking water except in cases of emergency. May be utilized to extinguish fires in forgeworks facility only - not to be used to extinguish fires in living quarters as these are non-critical emergencies.

Fuel required for classified projects.

Violators will be executed."
